OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,F"There's nothing worse than feeling
OL,8,Fyou can't provide for your own
OL,9,Fchildren, especially in winter you
OL,10,Fcan't even give them the heating
OL,11,Fthat's they require.
OL,13,F"They can't shower - we're having to
OL,14,Fboil kettles to have hot water for
OL,15,Fdishes - yeah it's been hard".
OL,17,FMichelle had her gas disconnected in
OL,18,FSeptember 2023, and said she struggled
OL,19,Fover the winter months.
