OL,7,FShe said: "I've been having these
OL,8,Fpressures for over twelve months now.
OL,9,FI used to think long term and plan
OL,10,Fthings and prioritise things and now
OL,11,Fit's just like I'm trying to survive
OL,12,Feach day."
OL,14,FIn the south of the island, Elizabeth
OL,15,Fis facing similar pressures looking
OL,16,Fafter her children, and believes there
OL,17,Fis still a stigma around asking for
OL,18,Fhelp.
