OL,7,FShe said: "People don't realise how
OL,8,Fmuch we are actually suffering with
OL,9,Fthe cost of living on the island."
OL,11,FOne of the initiatives tackling the
OL,12,Fcost of living is the 'Isle Pay it
OL,13,FForward' scheme, aimed at cafes around
OL,14,Fthe island.
OL,16,FCustomers have an option to donate
OL,17,Fmoney to the cafes, which then
OL,18,Feventually pays for those who are
OL,19,Fsigned up to the scheme.
