OL,7,FElizabeth regularly visits Cafe Red in
OL,8,FPort Erin, and says the scheme has
OL,9,Fchanged her life.
OL,11,FShe said: "I didn't really go
OL,12,Fanywhere, I wasn't very sociable. I
OL,13,Fkind of just stuck to me and my little
OL,14,Fboy in our own little bubble.
OL,16,F"But now it's just give me the go to
OL,17,Fget up and go out with him and
OL,18,Fsocialise a little bit more, because I
OL,19,Fstruggled terribly for like the last
OL,20,F15 years.
